Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as boosting is a popular technique in AI. The paper also mentions classification, which suggests it could be categorized under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper's focus on real-world practicability suggests it could be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
